snippet.title: [Amstrad CPC] Camelot Warriors - Longplay
snippet.description:
Camelot Warriors
© Dinamic Software (1986)

Never look back as thou entereth the four worlds of mystery.
The forest : A natural setting in which enemy forces await thee. A druid will cast will cast a spell on thou and transformeth thee to a slimy toad!
The lake : Killer fish, electric eels and a reign of terror will givest thou a shock to thy system.
The caves : Thou art buried underground and havest trouble breathing such stuffy air - thou must findeth the surface and quicketh!
Camelot castle : Thou must findeth the voice from the other world which will solveth this mystery.
All four worlds are interlinked and thou must findeth their frontier zones to passeth between them.
